flowchart TD
    A[Order PENDING dibuat] --> B[Enqueue order-expired-queue]
    A --> C[Enqueue unlock-seat-expired-queue]
    B --> D[Delay 1 jam]
    C --> E[Delay 1 jam]
    D --> F{Order sudah PAID?}
    F -- Ya --> G[Skip cancel]
    F -- Tidak --> H[Mark order expired/cancel]
    E --> I{Seat masih terkunci?}
    I -- Ya --> J[Unlock seat dari DepartureAvailability]
    I -- Tidak --> K[Skip unlock]
    H --> J
